title: Global Zakii Enterprises, LLC Recalls Canned Meat and Canned Poultry Products Produced without Benefit of Import Inspection
summary: EDITORS NOTE: - This release is being updated to include previously unaccounted for product increasing the weight from 100 to 174 pounds. WASHINGTON, Oct. 17, 2019 Global Zakii Enterprises, LLC, a Houston, Texas establishment, is recalling approximately 174 pounds of canned meat and canned poultry...
